email_generation.prompt_template:
Write a cold outreach email for a web development contractor.

Target: {business_name} ({bucket})
Website: {url}

Issues Found:
{issues}

Write a personalized email that:
1. Mentions their business specifically
2. Points out 1-2 key issues (not all)
3. Offers a solution without being pushy
4. Has a clear, low-pressure CTA
5. Keeps it under 150 words

Return ONLY JSON:
{{
  "subject": "<subject line under 50 chars>",
  "body": "<email body with greeting and signature>"
}}
